videoSnippet.title: Chess is Funny Like That | Karjakin vs Sevian | Isle of Man (2018)
videoSnippet.description:
Follow me on Instagram for extra content: https://www.instagram.com/agadmator/

Sergey Karjakin vs Samuel Sevian
Isle of Man Open Tournament, Round 5
25 Oct 2018.
Ruy Lopez: Morphy Defense (C88)
